00:49:04.180 --> 00:49:08.180
by starting off with a piece of straight bar,

00:49:08.180 --> 00:49:11.180
measure the horse's foot, cut the bar to the right size

00:49:11.180 --> 00:49:14.180
and then trim the horse's foot in readiness for it,

00:49:14.180 --> 00:49:19.180
make the shoe, fit it and apply it within a certain time.

00:49:19.180 --> 00:49:23.180
And they have to do that over a period of a couple of days on different horses,

00:49:23.180 --> 00:49:28.180
different types of horses, and always within a time limit.

00:49:28.180 --> 00:49:32.180
That's remarkable, things that you never even think about existing.

00:49:32.180 --> 00:49:35.180
I know, I know.

