00:49:57.180 --> 00:50:03.180
the levelness of the foot, the symmetry of the foot when it's been trimmed

00:50:03.180 --> 00:50:07.180
has to be very, very good, the levelness has to be good.

00:50:07.180 --> 00:50:12.180
Then when the shoe is made, it has to fit that foot exactly,

00:50:12.180 --> 00:50:17.180
and within a certain time.

